text: Jose Riano is a Filipino politician from the province of Romblon in the Philippines. He currently serves as a Governor of Romblon. He was first elected as Governor of the province in 2019 following the three terms of former Romblon Governor Eduardo Firmalo Chang. ==References== * * * * ==External links== *Province of Romblon Category:Living people Category:Governors of Romblon Category:1977 births Category:PDP–Laban politicians
